<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="gn1016b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="gn1" href="#gn1016">GN1 </a>  <a href="../../FF/unbs/gn1all.htm#gn1016b"> (Dzierbicki) 16(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> &ldquo;Why?&rdquo; <p class="flush">&ldquo;Because otherwise I could not see you.&rdquo;</p> <p class="flush">Sliding &mdash; space &mdash; ages &mdash; foliage of stars &mdash; and waning / heaven &mdash; stillness &mdash; and stillness deeper &mdash; stillness of / annihilation &mdash; and her voice.</p> </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: In <cite>Exiles</cite> Joyce gives the second line to Beatrice (see <a href="https://archive.org/details/in.ernet.dli.2015.509592/page/n21/mode/2up" target="_blank">page 20, line 9 from end</a> in the Jonathan Cape edition. </mm> </dd></dl>
